Cs_StoneTower_V2

This is the second version of the Stone Tower jump map. Its size is absolutely epic, just scraping the surface of the impossible limit of hammer editor's grid. Each screen shot is literally looking at around 1/20th of the entire map. This tower is designed to appeal to the general audience of Counter-Strike: Source, as it is easy to the point of basic skill, yet gets harder as you ascend. It's fun and requires teamwork, precise jumping techniques, and creative thinking. I currently need beta testers and would love to have you try it out. Please assess and provide constructive feedback.
